<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.4.5">
<l>tevvāya maṟamaṉṉar kuruti koṇṭu tirukkulatti liṟantōrkkut tirutti ceytu</l>
<l>vevvāya mākīṇṭu vēḻa maṭṭa viṇṇavarkōṉ tāḷaṇaivīr vikirta mātar</l>
<l>avvāya vāḷneṭuṅkaṇ kuvaḷai kāṭṭa varavintam mukaṅkāṭṭa varukē yāmpal</l>
<l>cevvāyiṉ tiraḷkāṭṭum vayalcūḻ kāḻic cīrāma viṇṇakarē cērmi ṉīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who clasp the feet of the celestials’ king who destroyed the elephant,</l>
<l rend="indent">having split the cruel-mouthed horse,</l>
<l>[And] having made appeasement [offerings] for the dead in his divine clan,</l>
<l rend="indent">bearing the blood of brave kings who had become enemies,</l>
<l>Gather you [all] at Cīrāmaviṇṇakaram in Kāḻi surrounded by fields where,</l>
<l rend="indent">as dark lilies show their long eyes such as of diverse ladies,</l>
<l>[And] as lotuses show [their] faces, nearby red lilies show a myriad of rosy lips.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
